modName: HMs ENB Series Settings with taxless SSAO and SMAA
summary: My custom settings of ENB 1.02. I tweaked SSAO and have almost no performance hit. There is also SMAA for us ATI Users.
descriptionHtml:
Hello all

I present to you my custom ENB settings which incluse SSAO and SMAA. The game looks gorgeous and with SSAO on there is almost no frame hit.

Feel free to add screenshots and endorse if you like :)

-HM
author: HellsMaster
